The full Dread Army is coming!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dorkfactory/thedreadarmy

Prepare yourself for a massive army bundle of pre-supported STLs that have returned from a hellish dimension.

Watch your foes tremble uncontrollably when they get their first glimpse of your terrifying army from across the tabletop.

The Dread Army Kickstarter is a huge army bundle with 9 brand new kits and 18 heavily discounted for a total of 27 modular and monopose kits -- and possibly more depending on stretch goals! Many of the modular kits are cross compatible so the possibilities for unique variations is immense.

The Dread Army has been a major Dorkfactory project for five years now, and the goal of this kickstarter is to complete it with a bang!

Take a look and follow the project on kickstarter to keep updated!

10mm scale leader of the Empire of Men. In case a griffon just isn't massive and majestic enough for you...

Mz4250s Dragon of Creation is an awesome model to work with, as it's already rigged for posing, so special thanks for that great model!

I flattened portions of the figure's tail for gluing to a base, and have included both a round 40mm base and a 40x20mm base as basing options. Hopefully the figure will balance. I haven't printed it yet, so I can't confirm. If it's not balanced, a metal washer base might keep it from tipping.
